comments: Vanderbilt (UTA) maintains his arms within the frame of his body and marginal body contact occurs as Fox (SAC) defends under the pick.
Barnes (SAC) places a resting forearm to Markkanen's (UTA) front as he loses control of the ball on his own.
Markkanen (UTA) and Murray (SAC) both come together as they pursue the loose ball and briefly become tangled up with neither having control of the ball.
Murray (SAC) is the last player to touch the ball on the jump ball.  The ball is awarded to UTA.
Sabonis (SAC) places his forearm to Conley's (UTA) front and marginal body contact occurs during his drive to the basket.
Vanderbilt (UTA) brings his hands toward Fox (SAC) and marginal contact occurs as Vanderbilt (UTA) releases away to roll.
Olynyk (UTA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Sabonis (SAC) slightly extends his arm agaisnt Olynyk's (UTA) arm and marginal arm contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Olynyk (UTA) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Sabonis (SAC) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Sabonis (SAC) places his hand to Clarkson's (UTA) front and immediately slides his hand off at the start of his drive.
Markkanen (UTA) hands off the ball in Huerter's (SAC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Huerter (SAC) brushes Clarkson's (UTA) side and marginal body contact occurs defending his driving shot attempt.
Clarkson (UTA) briefly grasps Huerter's (SAC) arm before correcting.
Clarkson (UTA) reaches across Barnes (SAC) and marginal body contact occurs during the drive.
Clarkson (UTA) comes to a pause as he comes off the screen and Okpala (SAC) runs through him. prior to the ball being released from OB.
Clarkson (UTA) establishes himself in Mitchell's (SAC) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Mitchell (SAC) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Clarkson's (UTA) arm.
Murray (SAC) and Olynyk (UTA) mutually engage and immediately disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Okpala (SAC) moves alongside Conley's (UTA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Clarkson (UTA) and Huerter (SAC) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Huerter (SAC) establishes himself in Vanderbilt's (UTA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Clarkson (UTA) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Fox's (SAC) arm after the release.
Markkanen (UTA) engages with Barnes (SAC) off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Markkanen (UTA) releases away to retrieve the entry pass.
Murray (SAC) makes contact with Markkanen's (UTA) elbow during his upward shooting motion, and the contact alters his jump shot attempt.
Markkanen (UTA) engages and disengages with Barnes (SAC) and marginal contact occurs prior to the pick being set.
Markkanen (UTA) places a bent forearm to Fox's (SAC) side and marginal body contact occurs contesting his driving shot attempt.
Sabonis (SAC) makes marginal contact to Olynyk's (UTA) side after the shot is completed.
Murray (SAC) places a stayed hand against Markkanen's (UTA) chest off ball and marginal contact occurs as he gathers the entry pass.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Markkanen's (UTA) shot attempt was overruled to a no basket. Markkanen (UTA) releases his shot attempt after the shot clock expires.
